title: Episode 357: The King of Raw...and B (Feat. Nick Cannon)
itunes:title: Episode 357: The King of Raw...and B (Feat. Nick Cannon)
description:
The legend himself, Nick Cannon joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his latest project "Raw & B." The crew speak on a range of topics including the differences in vaginas, that time Nick learned he had a big d**k, having a potential sex addiction, and much more. Nick even confesses to having more children on the way. Enjoy!
